Name: google_benchmark+
URL: https://github.com/google/benchmark
Version: 1.9.5
Revision: v1.9.5
License: Apache 2.0
License File: ../../../LICENSE
Security Critical: no
Description: Stubbed google_benchmark repository.
This is stubbed out because Fuchsia does not compile BoringSSL's benchmarks.
Stubbing this prevents downloading its transitive dependencies (like libpfm)
which are blocked by Fuchsia's offline build policy.
